snippet.title: Little Big Snake - New Maps Trailer! - Best io Snake game!
snippet.description:
With newly updated biomes in Little Big Snake, now is a great time to jump in on the action! 

With 100+ skins to choose from, you can always stand out in the snake battle arena!

Little Big Snake is available now in the browser as well as on the Google Play store and Apple App store for Free!

Browser: https://littlebigsnake.com/
Google Play: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=air.com.littlebigsnake.littlebigsnake
App Store: https://apps.apple.com/us/app/little-big-snake/id1441412472

Little Big Snake is also available on ioGames.Space! You can check it out here with tonnes of other ioGames: https://iogames.space/littlebigsnake-io
